IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR AQUARIUM USE:

This software is designed to control LED lighting for live aquarium environments.
While extensive safety measures have been implemented, users assume all
responsibility for:

1. The welfare and safety of aquatic life
2. Proper testing and validation of the system
3. Monitoring fish behavior during initial deployment
4. Maintaining appropriate lighting parameters for their specific species
5. Having backup lighting systems available

The authors and contributors are not liable for any harm to aquatic life,
property damage, or other consequences resulting from the use of this software.

Always prioritize the health and well-being of your aquarium inhabitants.
